data.description:
If you are 55 or older, and you like to live in a quit, safe, yet convenient community, you should come and visit all the houses on the market in this community. Remember, not all houses are the same, realtors always remind you: location! Location! And location! That means you can decorate the interior any way you wanted, but you can’t change the location that the house reside! You are going to live hear for a long time, better choose the one you like the most! let me know if you would like visit us, Good luck!




Neighborhood Description

Solera is a 55+ Gated Community with 24 hr. Guard. Located in the west of the city of Beaumont (French for "beautiful mountain"), one of the fastest growing suburb in the States in 2007. This house is located at the north boarder of this community, no other houses in front of this house; so you can enjoy the beautiful open mountain view from the front yard year round; the gated community is safe, quiet yet convenient: About 15 minutes drive to Casino Morongo for entertainment, and Cabazon outlet stores for shopping, local shopping plaza is only about 4 miles away, about 30 minutes away from Palm Spring; there is a 18 hole golf court just outside the community gate. The community has a heated outdoor pool & spa, tennis courts, & Bocce courts. Beautiful Club House has a large fitness room, walking track, game and meeting rooms, pool tables, and table tennis room. Del-Webb (A Pulte company) is the best builder of this kind in the States. The house, with beautiful cement roof, is built on a pre-stressed concrete slab for better stability. There is no exposed wood portion outside of the house, for better termite protection.10 foot ceiling let you feel roomy, energy efficient windows and walls. This most demanded Trillions Model has 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, large den/office just the right size for you, Corian kitchen counter tops with nature oak cabinets, all window sills, gas fireplace in great room, the kitchen and all hallways floor are tiled; both bedroom has large walk-in closet; wood shutters in several rooms, ceiling fans in 3 rooms. Landscaped back yard has many fruit trees.
